{"tid":1390232,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰略］遊擊戰 - 突襲地府銀行地舖","createTime":"2019-07-31T05:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T09:50:43.000Z","uid":55257,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eac03324b42684a1ed57ce9eeda84f7c606c108f","tid":1390232,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"7.28 發夢發到迷失方向，進不得又退不得，好似企係到等地獄鬼犬咬，仲要被咬死左40多位好人<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議發夢要有新策略，經過星期二晚一役的啓示：<br />\n<br />\n1. 發夢要有副本的實體目標 （犬屋、鬼國銀行地舖）<br />\n2. 完成任務一定要移玉步到下一個副本，想盡慶d可等到地獄犬隻放大臭屁先走，緊記不可賴死唔走<br />\n3. 任務不需暴力，但必有強烈的象征式（雞蛋🥚、美麗字體、連農陣」<br />\n4. 完全所有副本就必需關機休息叉電<br />\n<br />\n遊擊重點在於以最低成本給予最大壓力，一定要不被咬！"},{"pid":"e3e610fdff24ca87e1e4f3c94d0993610ebee9c7","tid":1390232,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:55:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/VfuWZd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfuWZd5.png&h=4576ca37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cSQ2oL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cSQ2oL.png&h=cef8ee5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"789123243a563b0562772665a0c21ebd125ba585","tid":1390232,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/VfuWZd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfuWZd5.png&h=4576ca37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<im